// Hazel your personal Ai companion 
Frontend:
- Vue 3 + TypeScript
- WebGPU for GPU acceleration
- WebAudio for voice processing
- Three.js for character visualization
- Live2D/VRM character models

Backend:
- Node.js + Hono (HTTP/WebSocket)
- PostgreSQL (user data, conversations)
- Redis (caching, real-time)
- LLM Integration (OpenAI, Claude, local models)

Platforms:
- Web (Browser PWA)
- Desktop (Electron/Tauri)
- Mobile (React Native/Capacitor)
